{"tid":262013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又跟女] 南亞擾民生事 香港市民怕怕兜路走","createTime":"2017-05-29T01:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T12:38:11.000Z","uid":23479,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"382766ff16dc931cf600577d3ba9adc2a73c91fc","tid":262013,"uid":23479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:56:19.000Z","msg":"深水埗南亞兵團罪案頻生，街坊怕怕！<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">姓郭中五女生表示，之前曾遭南亞人尾隨</span></strong></span>，故得悉今早又發生街頭群毆事件後，亦感到擔心。她往後會走大路，或「兜路走」避開他們。其姓王男友則指，以前跟友人於觀塘消遣時，同行的女性友人曾遭附近南亞人叫囂滋擾，當時遂乘搭的士離開。<br />\n<br />\n在深水埗上學的黃小姐指，自己家住元朗，平日在元朗區眼見不少南亞人士，目光奇怪兼不友善，故遇上他們時，多會「扮講電話」走過，或繞路走，形容「怕咗佢」。<br />\n<br />\n家住石硤尾的林小姐表示，間中亦會前往深水埗，惟夜深時會避免逛街，盡量提防，小心安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170502/bkn-20170502190733682-0502_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170502%2Fbkn-20170502190733682-0502_00822_001.html&d=x7kOj2Lfm3HXM5rpwBCJGJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f0721d19\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170502/bkn-20170502190733682-0502_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6a8d495009e6d96e060173d0662fe2e136ee8655","tid":262013,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T02:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76473475352cdf1d0019452df158770c256ca02e","tid":262013,"uid":8392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T02:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1cc0baaa16b4f37cfe0b73329209fb4c9ed4216","tid":262013,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T02:05:38.000Z","msg":"都唔明點解呢幾年來 南亞裔增長得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <